# Electron app build output. electron-vite emits to apps/flow-electron/out/
# on every dev run and build, and these files are not source. Listed
# explicitly because the matching `out/` glob would also catch any
# `out/` directory the package itself ever introduces by accident.
apps/flow-electron/out/
